Welcome to Mood Meal Finder! This application helps you discover delicious meals based on your current mood.

How It Works

  • Select your current mood from the available options
  • Browse through 3 curated meal recommendations
  • View detailed recipes and cooking instructions
  • Enjoy your meal!

Technologies Used

  • React.js for building the user interface
  • React Router for navigation
  • TheMealDB API for meal data
  • Tailwind CSS for styling

About the Developer

This project was created as a midterm assignment to demonstrate React concepts including components, props, state management, hooks, and API integration.
